                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon dioxide capturing and processing integrated method for flue gas discharged by natural gas boiler",
                    "一种天然气锅炉排放烟气的二氧化碳捕集加工一体化方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of carbon dioxide resource utilization, and discloses a carbon dioxide trapping and processing integrated method for flue gas discharged by a natural gas boiler, which comprises the following steps: gas in a flue enters an absorption tower after being subjected to desulfurization and alkali washing, an absorbent is adopted for absorption to obtain a rich solution, and the absorbent adopted in the absorption tower is an MEA-PEHA solution with the concentration ratio of 5: 5; the rich solution enters a carbon dioxide subsequent collection procedure or a carbon dioxide capture and hydrogenation methane preparation integrated reaction procedure; a collection procedure: regenerating the rich solution in a regeneration tower to obtain a barren solution, feeding the barren solution into an absorption tower, and carrying out heat exchange between the rich solution and the barren solution; an integrated reaction procedure: after passing through the heat exchanger, the rich liquid is desorbed in the desorption and hydrogenation integrated tower, and then is separated by the gas-liquid separator; after passing through the heat exchanger, the liquid exchanges heat with an absorbent which absorbs carbon dioxide and flows out of the absorption tower, and enters the absorption tower for absorption; and the separated gas is mixed with hydrogen and then enters a desorption and hydrogenation integrated tower and a hydrogenation reaction tower. The device disclosed by the invention has the advantages of high systematization degree and low energy consumption."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于二氧化碳资源化利用领域，公开了一种天然气锅炉排放烟气的二氧化碳捕集加工一体化方法，包括：烟道的气体经脱硫、碱洗后进入吸收塔，采用吸收剂吸收得到富液，吸收塔中采用的吸收剂为浓度比5:5的MEA‑PEHA溶液；富液进入二氧化碳后续收集程序或进入二氧化碳捕集加氢制甲烷一体化反应程序；收集程序：富液在再生塔中再生后得到贫液进入吸收塔，富液与贫液进行热交换；一体化反应程序：富液经换热器后在解吸加氢一体塔内解吸后经气液分离器分离后液体经换热器与吸收塔内流出的吸收了二氧化碳的吸收剂进行换热后进入到吸收塔内进行吸收；分离出的气体与氢气混合后进入解吸加氢一体塔和加氢反应塔。本发明的装置具有系统化程度高和能耗低的优点。"
                }
            ]
